title: Budget Studio
description: Affordable studio perfect for students or young professionals. Basic amenities but great location near public transport.

title: Mid-Range Apartment
description: Comfortable 2-bedroom apartment with standard amenities. Good value for money in a safe neighborhood.

title: Premium Condo
description: High-end condo with luxury finishes and full amenities. Concierge service and valet parking available.

title: Starter Home
description: Perfect first home for new families. 3 bedrooms with potential for expansion. Quiet suburban street.

title: Executive Townhouse
description: Upscale townhouse in gated community. Premium location with golf course views and country club access.

title: Artist Studio Loft
description: Creative space with high ceilings and excellent natural light. Perfect for artists, photographers, or designers.

title: Retirement Condo
description: Single-level condo perfect for seniors. Elevator access, grab bars installed, and close to medical facilities.

title: Vacation Rental
description: Seasonal rental near ski slopes. Fully furnished with fireplace and mountain views. Available winter months only.

title: Corporate Housing
description: Furnished apartment for business travelers and relocating executives. All utilities and internet included.

title: Student Housing
description: Shared house perfect for college students. 5 bedrooms, common areas, and study spaces. Near campus shuttle.
